{"tid":2329854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【神奇數據】最新失業率下跌！報6.3%！","createTime":"2020-12-17T13:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T14:24:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bd267a358295542df74fc145e9e45a703afdcd81","tid":2329854,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:47:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565820-20201217.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565820-20201217.htm&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28UngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=8e14d6a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565820-20201217.htm&h=15ca17c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565820-20201217.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n本港最新失業率為6.3%，較8至10月輕微回落0.1個百分點。最新就業不足率為3.4%，較8至10月回落0.4個百分點。勞工及福利局局長羅致光說，鑑於最近的本地第四波疫情，勞工市場的壓力料會在短期內再次上升。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光說，勞工市場在9月至11月仍然疲弱，儘管該段期間本地第三波疫情趨穩，勞工市場呈現輕微改善。總就業人數與上一個期間相比上升0.6%，失業人數下跌5.2%至24萬4300人。<br />\n<br />\n與8至10月比較，9至11月期間，零售、住宿及膳食服務業、教育業，以及藝術、娛樂及康樂活動業的失業率，有相對明顯的下跌。就業不足率方面，下跌主要見於建造業、零售、住宿及膳食服務業以及運輸業。<br />\n<br />\n按行業分析，與消費及旅遊相關行業，即是零售、住宿及膳食服務業，合計的失業率在9至11月較8至10月略為下跌1.1個百分點至10.1%。其中，餐飲服務活動業的失業率，由14.8%下跌至13.1%。"},{"pid":"4a4c713fa62a03a0b861c7ef0dfa4ee790c0b67f","tid":2329854,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef718cb34efae8802efe446bfda863ed677b539a","tid":2329854,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"其實失業率係點樣分行業黎計?<br />\n訪問個陣順手問埋受訪者係做開邊行?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31501429ee0dede9894c504165ce6f6f32a0055f","tid":2329854,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ef718cb34efae8802efe446bfda863ed677b539a","tid":2329854,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"其實失業率係點樣分行業黎計?<br />\n訪問個陣順手問埋受訪者係做開邊行?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"稅局咩都睇到晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91750cd444bb731a5727b14a3674d3e5bc49b8a5","tid":2329854,"uid":299514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:24:13.000Z","msg":"下個月咪知囉"}]}